he five major areas of security that concern the world today.  By working together, these agencies address security-related interests by promoting and implementing the different and serious policies of the current Gameland administration.</p>			<p>Until the street are safe I recommend that you keep one eye open and the other on the skies.  Look for trouble and be ever vigilant.   By doing this you are ensuring your future and the future of Gamelanders to come.</p>			<p>Best,<br />Tyrone Jarvis</p>		</div>	</div></div></div></body></html>